#: ../../../Users/user/manuscript-ocr-1/docs/sphinx/pipeline_usage.rst:4
#: c368162885934bf5affb2f4c4adc942c
msgid ""
"The pipeline is stage-based and passes one ``Page`` object through the "
"stages:"
msgstr ""
"Pipeline построен из этапов и передаёт один объект ``Page`` через все этапы:"

#: ../../../Users/user/manuscript-ocr-1/docs/sphinx/pipeline_usage.rst:6
#: 9d25059b3f0a44a98da0a1da76c3489f
msgid "``detector -> layout -> recognizer -> corrector``"
msgstr "``detector -> layout -> recognizer -> corrector``"

#: ../../../Users/user/manuscript-ocr-1/docs/sphinx/pipeline_usage.rst:8
#: eb69cc10add0413b8b3cf39956908acf
msgid "By default, ``Pipeline()`` creates:"
msgstr "По умолчанию ``Pipeline()`` создаёт:"

