msgstr "детектор: ``YOLO(weights=\"yolo26x_obb_text_g1\")``"

#: ../../../Users/user/manuscript-ocr-1/docs/sphinx/pipeline_usage.rst:11
#: 30976c5af1354e11941d0996919ef463
