msgstr "распознаватель: ``TRBA(weights=\"trba_lite_g2\")``"

#: ../../../Users/user/manuscript-ocr-1/docs/sphinx/pipeline_usage.rst:13
#: 4e86bb2f174142e78eb7ac4d2fa40f3c
